title: Cost of a liver transplant on the National Health Service in the United Kingdom 2015
summary: This bar chart has 6 categories for the x axis representing Cost in British pounds, and a y axis representing Share of respondents.
The highest category is found at 5000-10000 where Share of respondents is 21.0.
The lowest category is found at 2300-5000 where Share of respondents is 9.0.
